title: Sweden Hourly Wage Growth YoY
description: Wages in Sweden increased 2.80 percent in August of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Wage Growth in Sweden averaged 3.21 percent from 1992 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 7.10 percent in May of 1996 and a record low of 1.50 percent in June of 2020. This page provides - Sweden Wage Growth- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Swedish National Mediation Office
